I"z<p>ArcGIS API for JavaScript集成Echarts实现迁徙图效果的关键问题在于Echarts坐标系与ArcGIS坐标系不一致，需要进行Echarts坐标系与ArcGIS坐标系的转换。<br />
<!--more--></p>
<h2 id="功能">功能</h2>
<p>ArcGIS API for JavaScript集成Echarts实现迁徙图</p>
<h2 id="工具">工具</h2>
<ul>
  <li>ArcGIS API for JavaScript 4.15</li>
  <li>Echarts 4.70</li>
</ul>

<h2 id="思路">思路</h2>
<p>调用 <a href="https://developers.arcgis.com/javascript/latest/api-reference/esri-views-MapView.html">esri/views/MapView</a> 的 <a href="https://developers.arcgis.com/javascript/latest/api-reference/esri-views-MapView.html#toScreen">toScreen()</a> 方法将地理坐标转为屏幕坐标，然后通过Echarts可视化。</p>
